Related: Crowd Cache, Crowd Control, crowdfund, group, join, prepay, team, teem

Groups of diverse humans could create cells of productivity.

When property creates profit and that profit buys more property, a positive-feedback loop causes wealth to concentrate as an accidental side-effect of organizing production.

Corporate success is not so much cleverness as it is just a natural result of the power of organizing crowds to solve problems, though rarely for their own needs.

====Notes
Snowdrift.coop >>is a non-profit, cooperative platform for funding free/libre/open public goods of all sorts.

